query:
SELECT
                COALESCE(SUM(insertions), 0) as total_insertions,
                COALESCE(SUM(deletions), 0) as total_deletions,
                COUNT(DISTINCT author_email) as unique_authors,
                MIN(authored_at) as first_commit,
                MAX(authored_at) as last_commit
            FROM git_commits
            WHERE project_id = ?
